GRIT - A tool for the integrative analysis of RNA-seq type assays. 

INSTALL:

Dependencies

scipy
cython
python-igraph
python-networkx
pysam ( https://code.google.com/p/pysam/ )

Then, in the grit directory, run 

python setup.py build_ext --inplace

In ubuntu:
sudo aptitude install python-scipy python-igraph python-networkx cython
wget https://pysam.googlecode.com/files/pysam-0.7.5.tar.gzpython setup.py install
tar -zxvf pysam-0.7.5.tar.gz
cd pysam-0.7.5
sudo python setup.py install

Then, in the grit directory, python setup.py build_ext --inplace

Running GRIT:

Run 

bin/grit.py --help

options should be explained in the output. 